{
  "stem": "1316.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "They didn't believe her, the Germans-- the Ukrainians were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "But they said, she wanted  to join with her people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "They pushed her in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They-- the Jewish policeman, there were 100 Jewish policemen with their commandant, they helped to chase the Jews to bring them to the train.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And they guarded them with Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They hoped that they would survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They were standing, and their wife and children were put aside.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "So they hoped that their wives and children will survive.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "In the last minute, the German commandant said to push them in-- push their wives and children.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And the 100 policemen were standing and looking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "They didn't move.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "They thought they were saving their life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Only 1 of 100, only one policeman survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "His family goes into the wagon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "He threw his police hat, his police-- and he went into the wagon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And this is why he regrets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "He calls the book Now what happened-- what happened to him was the policeman were taken to a camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Finally, they were all shot, even the commandant was shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "He ran away-- he hid himself in Warsaw in hiding with a Polish woman.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "He was-- and he died in the uprising in 1944, when the Russians were at the shores of the Vistula.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "They waited, the Poles made an uprising, the Russians didn't intervene.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "They were all destroyed, and so on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "He died there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let me finish about him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the hiding, in three months, he wrote this book-- the memoir of what happened in the Otwock ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He sent it to our friend, the Polish friend, in Otwock.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He kept it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "After the war, his brother survived in Russia, came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took to the original copy to the Yad Vashem, to Israel.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
